					</p>
					<p>
						The objective of the brand is to offer delicious fast foods with
						local taste preferences at an affordable prices. The founders of
						Arnold Burger are fast foods lovers themselves who are eager to
						create a local brand catering to local taste while keeping western
						fast foods tradition.<br>
					</p>
					<p>
						Our burgers offer spicy chicken flavor, jumbo size chicken patty,
						whole fish meat patty, tasty beef patties serve with cheese,
						lettuce, tomato and sauces. Arnold’s chicken comes in 2 flavors :
						original and spicy. Our snacks offering are French Fries, Breaded
						Cheese Sticks, Tempura Chicken Nuggets and Breaded Calamari Rings
						which are much favored by kids.<br>
					</p>
					<p>
						Arnold instead of offering carbonated drinks which is deemed as
